import requests
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import csv

HOST = 'https://autogidas.lt/'
URL = 'https://autogidas.lt/skelbimai/automobiliai/'
HEADERS = {
    'Accept': 'text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,image/avif,image/webp,image/apng,*/*;q=0.8,application/signed-exchange;v=b3;q=0.7',
    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/115.0.0.0 Safari/537.36'
}

def get_html(url, params=''):
    r = requests.get(url, headers=HEADERS, params=params)
    return r


def get_content(response):
    if response.status_code == 403:
        print("Сайт блокирует доступ.")
    else:
        print(response.status_code)

    soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, 'html.parser')
    items = soup.find_all('main', class_='all-items-block content-section')
    cards = []

    for item in items:
        title_element = item.find('article', class_='list-item').find('a').find('div', class_='right').find('div', class_='description').find('h2').get_text()
        #title = title_element.get_text() if title_element else "Нет информации о заголовке"

        toplivo = item.find('article', class_='list-item').find('a').get('href')

        city_element = item.find('div', class_='announcement-parameters')
        city = city_element.find_all('span')[0].get_text(strip=True) if city_element else "Нет информации о городе"

        link_product_element = item.find('a', class_='adsImage js-cfuser-link')
        link_product = link_product_element.get('href') if link_product_element else "Нет ссылки на продукт"

        fuel = city_element.find_all('span')[0].get_text(strip=True) if city_element else "Нет информации о топливе"

        cards.append({
            'title_element': title_element,
            'toplivo': toplivo,
            'city': city,
            'link_product': link_product,
            'fuel': fuel
        })

    return cards



html = get_html(URL)
print(get_content(html))

title: json
content:
------------------------------------------------------------------ utils
local controls = {["\n"]="\\n", ["\r"]="\\r", ["\t"]="\\t", ["\b"]="\\b", ["\f"]="\\f", ["\""]="\\\"", ["\\"]="\\\\"}

local function isArray(t)
	local max = 0
	for k,v in pairs(t) do
		if type(k) ~= "number" then
			return false
		elseif k > max then
			max = k
		end
	end
	return max == #t
end

local whites = {['\n']=true; ['\r']=true; ['\t']=true; [' ']=true; [',']=true; [':']=true}
function removeWhite(str)
	while whites[str:sub(1, 1)] do
		str = str:sub(2)
	end
	return str
end

------------------------------------------------------------------ encoding

local function encodeCommon(val, pretty, tabLevel, tTracking)
	local str = ""

	-- Tabbing util
	local function tab(s)
		str = str .. ("\t"):rep(tabLevel) .. s
	end

	local function arrEncoding(val, bracket, closeBracket, iterator, loopFunc)
		str = str .. bracket
		if pretty then
			str = str .. "\n"
			tabLevel = tabLevel + 1
		end
		for k,v in iterator(val) do
			tab("")
			loopFunc(k,v)
			str = str .. ","
			if pretty then str = str .. "\n" end
		end
		if pretty then
			tabLevel = tabLevel - 1
		end
		if str:sub(-2) == ",\n" then
			str = str:sub(1, -3) .. "\n"
		elseif str:sub(-1) == "," then
			str = str:sub(1, -2)
		end
		tab(closeBracket)
	end

	-- Table encoding
	if type(val) == "table" then
		assert(not tTracking[val], "Cannot encode a table holding itself recursively")
		tTracking[val] = true
		if isArray(val) then
			arrEncoding(val, "[", "]", ipairs, function(k,v)
				str = str .. encodeCommon(v, pretty, tabLevel, tTracking)
			end)
		else
			arrEncoding(val, "{", "}", pairs, function(k,v)
				assert(type(k) == "string", "JSON object keys must be strings", 2)
				str = str .. encodeCommon(k, pretty, tabLevel, tTracking)
				str = str .. (pretty and ": " or ":") .. encodeCommon(v, pretty, tabLevel, tTracking)
			end)
		end
	-- String encoding
	elseif type(val) == "string" then
		str = '"' .. val:gsub("[%c\"\\]", controls) .. '"'
	-- Number encoding
	elseif type(val) == "number" or type(val) == "boolean" then
		str = tostring(val)
	else
        str = 'null'
		-- error("JSON only supports arrays, objects, numbers, booleans, and strings", 2)
	end
	return str
end

function encode(val)
	return encodeCommon(val, false, 0, {})
end

function encodePretty(val)
	return encodeCommon(val, true, 0, {})
end

------------------------------------------------------------------ decoding

local decodeControls = {}
for k,v in pairs(controls) do
	decodeControls[v] = k
end

function parseBoolean(str)
	if str:sub(1, 4) == "true" then
		return true, removeWhite(str:sub(5))
	else
		return false, removeWhite(str:sub(6))
	end
end

function parseNull(str)
	return nil, removeWhite(str:sub(5))
end

local numChars = {['e']=true; ['E']=true; ['+']=true; ['-']=true; ['.']=true}
function parseNumber(str)
	local i = 1
	while numChars[str:sub(i, i)] or tonumber(str:sub(i, i)) do
		i = i + 1
	end
	local val = tonumber(str:sub(1, i - 1))
	str = removeWhite(str:sub(i))
	return val, str
end

function parseString(str)
	str = str:sub(2)
	local s = ""
	while str:sub(1,1) ~= "\"" do
		local next = str:sub(1,1)
		str = str:sub(2)
		assert(next ~= "\n", "Unclosed string")

		if next == "\\" then
			local escape = str:sub(1,1)
			str = str:sub(2)

			next = assert(decodeControls[next..escape], "Invalid escape character")
		end

		s = s .. next
	end
	return s, removeWhite(str:sub(2))
end

function parseArray(str)
	str = removeWhite(str:sub(2))

	local val = {}
	local i = 1
	while str:sub(1, 1) ~= "]" do
		local v = nil
		v, str = parseValue(str)
		val[i] = v
		i = i + 1
		str = removeWhite(str)
	end
	str = removeWhite(str:sub(2))
	return val, str
end

function parseObject(str)
	str = removeWhite(str:sub(2))

	local val = {}
	while str:sub(1, 1) ~= "}" do
		local k, v = nil, nil
		k, v, str = parseMember(str)
		val[k] = v
		str = removeWhite(str)
	end
	str = removeWhite(str:sub(2))
	return val, str
end

function parseMember(str)
	local k = nil
	k, str = parseValue(str)
	local val = nil
	val, str = parseValue(str)
	return k, val, str
end

function parseValue(str)
	local fchar = str:sub(1, 1)
	if fchar == "{" then
		return parseObject(str)
	elseif fchar == "[" then
		return parseArray(str)
	elseif tonumber(fchar) ~= nil or numChars[fchar] then
		return parseNumber(str)
	elseif str:sub(1, 4) == "true" or str:sub(1, 5) == "false" then
		return parseBoolean(str)
	elseif fchar == "\"" then
		return parseString(str)
	elseif str:sub(1, 4) == "null" then
		return parseNull(str)
	end
	return nil
end

function decode(str)
	str = removeWhite(str)
	t = parseValue(str)
	return t
end

function decodeFromFile(path)
	local file = assert(fs.open(path, "r"))
	local decoded = decode(file.readAll())
	file.close()
	return decoded
end

content:
local ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
local SSS = game:GetService("ServerScriptService")
local SS = game:GetService("ServerStorage")
local Players = game:GetService("Players")

local Remotes = ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild("Remotes")
local deletePartRemote = Remotes:FindFirstChild("DeletePart")

local Bindables = SSS:FindFirstChild("Bindables")
local giveItemBindable = Bindables:FindFirstChild("GiveItem")

local items = SS:FindFirstChild("Items")

local PlayerStats = {
	Batteries = {Type = "Number", Value = 1},
	CollectedItems = {Type = "Int", Value = 0},
	UsedFlashlight = {Type = "Bool", Value = false}
}

Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(plr)
	local statFolder = Instance.new("Folder")
	statFolder.Name = "stats"
	statFolder.Parent = plr
	
	for i,v in pairs(PlayerStats) do
		local stat = Instance.new(`{v.Type}Value`)
		stat.Name = i
		stat.Value = v.Value
		stat.Parent = statFolder
	end
end)

giveItemBindable.OnInvoke = function(plr, itemName)
	if not plr then return false end
	if not plr.Parent then return false end
	
	local item = items:FindFirstChild(itemName)
	if not item then return false end
	
	local backpack = plr:FindFirstChildOfClass("Backpack")
	if not backpack then return false end
	
	item:Clone().Parent = backpack
	
	return true
end

title: 250 Rooms UIScript
content:
local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
local ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
local TwS = game:GetService("TweenService")

local function tween(obj,_time,props,yield,es,ed)TwS:Create(obj,TweenInfo.new(_time, es, ed),props):Play()if yield then wait(_time) end end

local function toMSMs(s)
	return string.format("%02i:%02i.%02i", s/60, s%60, s*100%100)
end

local Remotes = ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild("Remotes")

local speedrunTeleportRemote = Remotes:FindFirstChild("SpeedrunTele")
local jumpscareRemote = Remotes:FindFirstChild("Jumpscare")
local clientFXRemote = Remotes:FindFirstChild("ClientFX")

local plr = Players.LocalPlayer

local statsFolder = plr:WaitForChild("stats")
local batteriesStat = statsFolder:WaitForChild("Batteries")

RunService.Heartbeat:Connect(function()
	script.Parent.BatteryCount.Text = math.floor(batteriesStat.Value)
	
	script.Parent.BatteryFrame["5"].Visible = (batteriesStat.Value % 1 > 0.8) or (batteriesStat.Value % 1 == 0 and batteriesStat.Value >= 1)
	script.Parent.BatteryFrame["4"].Visible = batteriesStat.Value % 1 > 0.6 or (batteriesStat.Value % 1 == 0 and batteriesStat.Value >= 1)
	script.Parent.BatteryFrame["3"].Visible = batteriesStat.Value % 1 > 0.4 or (batteriesStat.Value % 1 == 0 and batteriesStat.Value >= 1)
	script.Parent.BatteryFrame["2"].Visible = batteriesStat.Value % 1 > 0.2 or (batteriesStat.Value % 1 == 0 and batteriesStat.Value >= 1)
	script.Parent.BatteryFrame["1"].Visible = batteriesStat.Value > 0
	
	local timerVar = ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild("TimerVar")
	
	script.Parent.TimerText.Visible = not not timerVar
	script.Parent.BatteryFrame.Visible = not timerVar
	script.Parent.BatteryCount.Visible = math.floor(batteriesStat.Value) >= 1 and not timerVar
	
	if timerVar then
		script.Parent.TimerText.Text = tostring(timerVar.Value)
	end
	
	local speedrunVar = ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild("SpeedrunVar")
	
	script.Parent.SpeedrunFrame.Visible = not not speedrunVar
	
	if speedrunVar then
		script.Parent.SpeedrunFrame:FindFirstChild("Clock").Text = toMSMs(speedrunVar.Value)
	end
end)

jumpscareRemote.OnClientEvent:Connect(function(image, sound, fadeStartScaledTime, fadeEndScaledTime, parameters)
	script.Parent.JumpscareImage.Image = image
	script.Parent.JumpscareImage.Position = UDim2.new(.5, -(script.Parent.JumpscareImage.AbsoluteSize.X / 2), 0, 0)
	
	script.Parent.JumpscareImage.ImageTransparency = 0
	script.Parent.BlackBG.BackgroundTransparency = 0
	
	local sfx = script.Parent:FindFirstChild(sound)
	
	sfx:Play()
	
	if parameters.AfterSound then
		task.spawn(function()
			task.wait(sfx.TimeLength * parameters.AfterSoundScaledPlayTime)
			local afterSfx = script.Parent:FindFirstChild(parameters.AfterSound)
			afterSfx:Play()
		end)
	end
	
	while sfx.TimePosition < sfx.TimeLength * fadeStartScaledTime do
		script.Parent.JumpscareImage.Position = UDim2.new(.5 + math.random(-10, 10) / 100, -(script.Parent.JumpscareImage.AbsoluteSize.X / 2), 0, 0)
		script.Parent.JumpscareImage.Rotation = math.random(-20, 20)
		wait(.1)
	end
	
	tween(script.Parent.JumpscareImage, fadeEndScaledTime - fadeStartScaledTime, {ImageTransparency = 1}, false, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear, Enum.EasingDirection.In)
	tween(script.Parent.BlackBG, fadeEndScaledTime - fadeStartScaledTime, {BackgroundTransparency = 1}, false, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear, Enum.EasingDirection.In)
end)

clientFXRemote.OnClientEvent:Connect(function(key, value, value2)
	if key == "whiteflash" then
		local whiteBG = script.Parent:FindFirstChild("WhiteBG"):Clone()
		whiteBG.Name = "WhiteBGFlash"
		whiteBG.BackgroundTransparency = value2
		whiteBG.Parent = script.Parent
		
		tween(whiteBG, value, {BackgroundTransparency = 1}, false, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear, Enum.EasingDirection.Out)
	end
end)

title: 250 Rooms EntityManager Script
content:
local SSS = game:GetService("ServerScriptService")
local SS = game:GetService("ServerStorage")
local TS = game:GetService("TweenService")

local Bindables = SSS:FindFirstChild("Bindables")
local spawnEntityBindable = Bindables:FindFirstChild("SpawnEntity")

local Entities = SS:FindFirstChild("Entities")

local function tween(obj,_time,props,yield,es,ed)TS:Create(obj,TweenInfo.new(_time, es, ed),props):Play()if yield then wait(_time) end end

spawnEntityBindable.Event:Connect(function(entityName, room, properties)
	if not room then return end
	
	local entity = Entities:FindFirstChild(entityName)
	if not entity then return end
	
	if not properties then return end
	
	local distance = properties.Distance or math.random(1000, 1500)
	local speed = properties.Speed or 125
	
	local floor = room:FindFirstChild("Floor")
	if not floor then return end
	
	local entityClone = entity:Clone()
	entityClone.Name = properties.Name or "ENTITY"
	entityClone.Position = floor.Position + Vector3.new(0, 10, distance)
	entityClone.Parent = workspace
	
	entityClone.Touched:Connect(function(part)
		local pointLight = part:FindFirstChildOfClass("PointLight")
		local spotLight = part:FindFirstChildOfClass("SpotLight")
		
		if pointLight then
			pointLight.Enabled = false
		end
		
		if spotLight then
			spotLight.Enabled = false
		end
		
		if string.sub(part.Name, 1, 12) == "VendingLight" then
			part.Color = Color3.new(0, 0, 0)
		end
	end)
	
	tween(entityClone, math.abs(distance / speed), {Position = Vector3.new(entityClone.Position.X, entityClone.Position.Y, floor.Position.Z)}, true, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.In)
	tween(entityClone, math.abs(distance / speed), {Position = Vector3.new(entityClone.Position.X, entityClone.Position.Y, floor.Position.Z - distance)}, true, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out)
	
	entityClone:Destroy()
end)

content:
---

- hosts: localhost
  connection: local
  gather_facts: false
  vars:
    wallix_url: https://wallix.ninja.cybersoprasteria.com
    wallix_username: adm.fmangeant
    wallix_password: xxxxxxxxxxxxx
    wallix_newuser:
        name: fmt
        email: frederic.mangeant@gmail.com
        comment: Ansible created user
        group: admins
        profil: user
    smtp_host: smtp.gmail.com
    smtp_port: 465
    smtp_username: toto@gmail.com
    smtp_password: xxxxxxxx
    onetimesecret_url: https://onetimesecret.com
    onetimesecret_username: toto@gmail.com
    onetimesecret_apitoken: xxxxxx
    onetimesecret_ttl: 86400
  tasks:
    - debug:
        msg: 'user : {{ smtp_username }} / password : {{ smtp_password }}'

    - name: Generate multiple random strings
      set_fact:
        random_digits: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=4 chars=digits') }}"
        random_letters: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=4 chars=ascii_letters') }}"
        random_punctuation: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=4 chars=punctuation') }}"

    - name: Generate a random password
      shell: 'echo "{{ random_digits }}" "{{ random_letters }}" "{{ random_punctuation }}" | shuf'
      changed_when: false
      register: strings_shuffled

    - name: Search for {{ wallix_newuser.name }} user
      uri:
        method: GET
        url: '{{ wallix_url }}/api/users/?q=user_name~{{ wallix_newuser.name }}'
        validate_certs: false
        force_basic_auth: true
        url_username: '{{ wallix_username }}'
        url_password: '{{ wallix_password }}'
      register: users_list

    - name: Ensure {{ wallix_newuser.name }} is created and is member of {{ wallix_newuser.group }} group
      block:
        - name: Search for {{ wallix_newuser.group }} group
          uri:
            method: GET
            validate_certs: false
            url: '{{ wallix_url }}/api/usergroups/{{ wallix_newuser.group }}'
            force_basic_auth: true
            url_username: '{{ wallix_username }}'
            url_password: '{{ wallix_password }}'
          ignore_errors: true
          register: groups_list

        - name: Add {{ wallix_newuser.group }} group
          uri:
            method: POST
            validate_certs: false
            url: '{{ wallix_url }}/api/usergroups/'
            force_basic_auth: true
            url_username: '{{ wallix_username }}'
            url_password: '{{ wallix_password }}'
            body_format: json
            body: "{
              'group_name': '{{ wallix_newuser.group }}',
              'timeframes': [
              'allthetime'
                ],
              }"
            status_code: 204
          when: 'groups_list.json.error is defined and "Resource not found" in groups_list.json.error'

        # Methode 1
        - name: Generate a random password
          set_fact:
            random_password: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=16 chars=ascii_letters,digits,punctuation') }}"

        # Methode 2
        - name: Generate a random string
          shell: < /dev/urandom tr -cd "[:print:]" | head -c 16; echo
          changed_when: false
          register: new_password

        - name: Set a random password
          set_fact:
            random_password: '{{ new_password.stdout }}'

        # Methode 3
        - name: Generate multiple random strings
          set_fact:
            random_digits: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=4 chars=digits') }}"
            random_letters: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=4 chars=ascii_letters') }}"
            random_punctuation: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=4 chars=punctuation') }}"

        - name: Shuffle strings
          shell: 'echo {{ random_digits }} {{ random_letters }} {{ random_punctuation }} | shuf'
          changed_when: false
          register: strings_shuffled

        - name: Set a random password
          set_fact:
            random_password: '{{ strings_shuffled.stdout }}'

        - name: Add {{ wallix_newuser.name }} user
          uri:
            method: POST
            validate_certs: false
            url: '{{ wallix_url }}/api/users'
            force_basic_auth: true
            url_username: '{{ wallix_username }}'
            url_password: '{{ wallix_password }}'
            body_format: json
            body: "{
              'user_name': '{{ wallix_newuser.name }}',
              'email': '{{ wallix_newuser.email }}',
              'profile': '{{ wallix_newuser.profil }}',
              'password': '{{ random_password }}',
              'user_auths': [
              'local_password'
                ],
              'groups': [
              '{{ wallix_newuser.group }}'
                ],
              }"
            status_code: 204

        - name: Generate a random passphrase for OneTimeSecret.com
          set_fact:
            onetimesecret_passphrase: "{{ lookup('password', '/dev/null length=16 chars=ascii_letters,ascii_uppercase,ascii_lowercase,digits') }}"

        - name: Create a link using OneTimeSecret.com
          uri:
            method: POST
            url: '{{ onetimesecret_url }}/api/v1/share'
            url_username: '{{ onetimesecret_username }}'
            url_password: '{{ onetimesecret_apitoken }}'
            force_basic_auth: true
            body_format: form-urlencoded
            body:
              passphrase: '{{ onetimesecret_passphrase }}'
              ttl: "{{ onetimesecret_ttl }}"
              secret: '{{ random_password }}'
          register: onetimesecret_secret

        - name: Send an email to the user
          mail:
            host: '{{ smtp_host }}'
            port: '{{ smtp_port }}'
            username: '{{ smtp_username }}'
            password: '{{ smtp_password }}'
            subject: 'Your credentials on {{ wallix_url }}'
            from: '{{ smtp_username }}'
            to: '{{ wallix_newuser.email }}'
            body: 'Your password is available here : {{ onetimesecret_url }}/secret/{{ onetimesecret_secret.json.secret_key }}

            Passphrase : {{ onetimesecret_passphrase }}

            Expiration in 24 hours.'
      when: users_list.json[0].user_name is not defined
